SONotifier
----------

This project is a Mac OSX status bar application for displaying information regarding your (or other person) account in one of the StackExchange sites.

The application currently shows:
- Reputation (day/week/month/quarter/year/overall)
- Badge count.
- Latest reputation changes.
- Recent questions in the site.

Soon to be added:
- Settings:
  - Switching user (done)
  - Changing update intervals (done)
  - Favorite tags for new questions
- Hot questions
- Latest comments
- Login (??)

Requirements:
- Mac OSX 10.7.

The application is based on StackExchange API 2.0, (docs may be found at http://api.stackexchange.com/).
